AddressInfo.Title: Irene Village Mall (Irene)
AddressInfo.AddressLine1: Cnr of Nellmapius Dr and Van Ryneveld Ave, Irene
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Main Entry Point	
Enter through the boom into Mezereon Cresent, drive to the ramp in the middle of the parking lot to enter the lower level. Once in the basement parking, drive towards the centre, after 40m to your right the charge point will be visible.

GeneralComments: Here you can take your time and shop at leisure in over 90 shops. In the basement parking, drive towards the centre. After 40m the DC fast charger will be visible on your right.
